modules/observability/__tests__/coverage-gate.test.ts` (NEW) — 14 unit tests\n   224→- `src/commands/__tests__/observability-gate.test.ts` (NEW) — 21 unit tests\n   225→- `src/__tests__/cli.test.ts` (MODIFIED) — updated command count to 22\n   226→- `tests/observability_gate_hook.bats` (NEW) — 4 BATS integration tests\n   227→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01KzBPVk4USrnjun4pqSYxZv","session_id":"c5eaf6a6-ac7c-4707-b82c-6220d711aa9c","uuid":"030fd3e3-6a24-4409-91de-d118657adbe9","timestamp":"2026-03-20T06:33:50.238Z"}
