{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_014GgkY57veGpsx2XzoZjuQ8","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01V8YoJKG7ctnXeaokPPKwRQ","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"### 2-3-standalone-runtime-check-audit-mode — dev-story (2026-03-20T06:43Z)","new_string":"### 2-3-standalone-runtime-check-audit-mode — code-review (2026-03-20T06:50Z)\n\n- **HIGH: Command injection** — `execSync(cfg.testCommand)` executed unsanitized user input. Fixed with metacharacter rejection.\n- **HIGH: Query timeout too short** — 3s health timeout reused for queries. Fixed with 30s query-specific timeout.\n- **MEDIUM: Malformed URL crash** — `new URL()` in `queryTelemetryEvents` could throw. Fixed with try/catch.\n- **LOW (not fixed): File grew to 212 lines** — story target was 200. Justified by security hardening.\n- **LOW (not fixed): `parseLogEvents` silently drops malformed JSON** — no counter or warning.\n- **LOW (not fixed): Substring module matching** — `event.source.includes(mod)` can false-positive on short names.\n- **Architecture: `saveRuntimeCoverage` doesn't persist module details** — Story 3.1 must address.\n\n### 2-3-standalone-runtime-check-audit-mode — dev-story (2026-03-20T06:43Z)"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1559,"cache_read_input_tokens":47478,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1559},"output_tokens":24,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c5eaf6a6-ac7c-4707-b82c-6220d711aa9c","uuid":"555d607f-95f1-46d5-9fff-31a7f1aa1caf"}
